  "The natural exponential function is e^x, where e (Euler's number) is approximately 2.71828. Its unique property is that d/dx[e^x] = e^x -- it is its own derivative.": "自然指数函数为ex,e(Euler的编号)约为2.71828,其独特的属性是d/dx[ex] = ex -- -- 它是其自身的衍生物。",
  "What does 'natural logarithm' (ln) mean?": "\"自然对数\"是什么意思?",
