  "log_a(x) = ln(x) / ln(a)": "log_a(x) = In(x) / in(a)",
  "The change of base formula states log_a(x) = ln(x)/ln(a). This is useful for differentiating logarithms of any base: d/dx[log_a(x)] = 1/(x*ln(a)).": "基公式的更改 log_a(x) = IN(x)/ln(a) 。这对区分任何基数的对数有用: d/dx[log_a(x)] = 1/(x*ln(a) ) 。",
  "What does 'inverse function' mean in the context of e^x and ln(x)?": "“反向函数”在 ex 和 In(x) 的背景中意味着什么 ?",
  "They have the same graph": "他们有相同的图表",
  "They multiply to one: e^x * ln(x) = 1": "它们乘以 1 : ex * In(x) = 1",
  "Each undoes the other: e^(ln(x)) = x and ln(e^x) = x": "相互对换 : e( ln( x)) = x 和 In( ex) = x",
  "They add to zero: e^x + ln(x) = 0": "它们增加为零: exx + In(x) = 0",
  "Two functions are inverses if each undoes the effect of the other. For e^x and ln(x): e^(ln(x)) = x for x > 0, and ln(e^x) = x for all x. Their graphs are reflections across the line y = x.": "两个函数是反向的,如果每个函数都折射其他函数的效果。对于 ex 和 In(x) : e(ln(x)) = x x x > 0, 而对于所有 x , In(ex) = x。它们的图表是横跨 y = x 的反射。",
  "What does 'logarithmic differentiation' mean?": "\"同义差异\"是什么意思?",
  "Converting all functions to logarithmic form": "将所有函数转换为对数窗体",
  "Taking the derivative of log functions only": "只取日志函数的衍生物",
