  "Differentiating using the quotient rule": "使用商数规则进行区分",
  "Logarithmic differentiation involves taking ln of both sides of y = f(x), then differentiating using properties of logarithms. It simplifies differentiation of products, quotients, and functions of the form f(x)^g(x).": "对数区分是指在y = f(x) 的两侧取用,然后使用对数特性加以区分。它简化了对产品、商数和表f(x)\\g(x)的函数的区分。",
  "What does 'asymptote' mean for exponential and logarithmic functions?": "指数函数和对数函数的“ 暂停” 是什么意思 ?",
