  "A point where the function reaches its maximum": "函数达到其最大值的点",
  "An asymptote is a line the graph approaches but never reaches. For e^x, y = 0 is a horizontal asymptote as x approaches negative infinity. For ln(x), x = 0 is a vertical asymptote.": "渐变图是一个直线, 直线是图形方法, 但无法达到。 对于 e x, y = 0 是一个水平的渐变图, 如 x 接近负无穷。 对于 In( x), x = 0 是垂直的渐变图 。",
  "A colony of bacteria doubles every 4 hours and starts with 500 cells. The population is P(t) = 500 * 2^(t/4). What is the growth rate at t = 8 hours?": "P(t) = 500 * 2(t/4). t = 8小时的增长率是多少?",
