  "A radioactive substance decays according to A(t) = 100e^(-0.05t) grams, where t is in years. How fast is it decaying at t = 10 years?": "放射性物质根据A(t) = 100e(- 0.05t) 克衰减,吨在几年之内。T = 10 年的衰减速度有多快?",
