  "An investment grows continuously at 6% per year. If the initial investment is $10,000, modeled by A(t) = 10000e^(0.06t), how fast is it growing after 5 years?": "投资以每年6%的速度持续增长。 如果初始投资为10 000美元,以A(t) = 10 000e(0.06t)为模型,那么五年后增长的速率是多少?",
