  "A'(t) = 10000 * 0.06 * e^(0.06t) = 600e^(0.06t). At t = 5: A'(5) = 600e^(0.3) per year (approximately $809.86/year).": "A'(t)=10000 * 0.06 * e(0.06t) = 600e(0.06t).at t = 5: A'(5) = 600e(0.3)/年(约809.86/年)。",
  "The pH of a solution is given by pH = -log_10[H+], where [H+] is the hydrogen ion concentration. If [H+] is increasing at a rate of 0.001 mol/L per second, how fast is the pH changing when [H+] = 0.01 mol/L?": "溶液的pH值由pH= -log_10[H+]给出,其中氢离子浓度为[H+]。如果[H+]以0.001 mol/L/秒的速度增长,pH值变化的速度是多少?",
