  "A cup of coffee cools according to Newton's Law: T(t) = 22 + 68e^(-0.1t) degrees Celsius. At what rate is the coffee cooling when its temperature is 56 degrees?": "根据牛顿法 : T(t) = 22 + 68e(-0.1t) 摄氏度。当咖啡温度为56度时,冷却速率是多少?",
