  "-6.8 degrees/min": "- 6.8度/分钟",
  "First find when T = 56: 56 = 22 + 68e^(-0.1t), so 34 = 68e^(-0.1t), e^(-0.1t) = 0.5. T'(t) = -6.8e^(-0.1t). When T = 56, e^(-0.1t) = 0.5, so T' = -6.8(0.5) = -3.4 degrees/min.": "当 T = 56: 56 = 22 + 68e(-0.1t), 所以 34 = 68e(-0.1t), e(-0.1t) = 0.5。 T'(t) = - 6.8e(-0.1t) 。 当 T = 56, e(-0.1t) = 0.5, 所以 T' = - 6.8(0.5) = - 3.4 度/分钟时, 第一次发现 T = 56, e(-0.1t) = 0.5, 所以 T' = - 6.8(0.5) = - 3.4 度/分钟。",
  "The decibel level of sound is L = 10 * ln(I/I_0)/ln(10), where I is intensity. If I = 0.001 watts/m^2 is increasing at 0.0001 watts/m^2 per second, what is dL/dt?": "L=10 * In(I_0)/ln(10),音频的分贝水平为10。如果I=0.001瓦特/平方米,每秒0.0001瓦特/平方米,什么是dL/dt?",
  "10 * 0.0001": "10 *0.0001",
